<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>컴퓨터 활용 콘텐츠 선택</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
    <script src="https://apis.google.com/js/api.js"></script>
    <style>
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .btn-group .btn {
            flex: 1;
            margin: 2px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center">컴퓨터 활용 콘텐츠 선택</h1>
        <div class="row" id="content-container">
            <!-- 카드를 동적으로 생성하는 부분 -->
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='https://studio.code.org/s/pre-express-2022/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">마우스 클릭연습(기초)</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">마우스 클릭연습</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/pre-express-2022/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='https://blockly.games/puzzle?lang=ko'">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">마우스 클릭연습(블럭)</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">블럭에 속성을 입력하여 알맞게 코딩해보세요</p>
                        <a href="https://blockly.games/puzzle?lang=ko" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='https://studio.code.org/s/aquatic/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">수중세계 탐험</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">수중 세계를 탐험하며 문제 해결 능력을 발휘해보세요.</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/aquatic/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100" onclick="location.href='https://studio.code.org/s/hero/lessons/1/levels/1'">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">히어로의 여정</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">에이전트에게 명령을 내리고 장애물을 극복하세요</p>
                        <a href="https://studio.code.org/s/hero/lessons/1/levels/1" class="btn btn-primary">시작하기</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 다른 카드들도 위와 같은 방식으로 추가 -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/header.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
